1
00:00:04,286 --> 00:00:07,760
In this module, we'll talk about 
diseases caused by unsafe water,

2
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:10,917
sanitation and hygiene, 
and how they can be classified,

3
00:00:10,917 --> 00:00:15,294
as well as the burden of disease due to
unsafe water, sanitation, hygiene,

4
00:00:15,294 --> 00:00:17,716
both in terms of deaths or mortality

5
00:00:17,716 --> 00:00:19,652
and disease or morbidity.

6
00:00:20,232 --> 00:00:24,584
They say that three things in life 
are certain: birth, taxes and death,

7
00:00:24,584 --> 00:00:28,441
