are those caused by parasites

44
00:02:35,551 --> 00:02:38,300
which live part of their 
life cycle in water.

45
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:42,513
The most serious of this 
is the Schistosomiasis or Billharzia

46
00:02:42,513 --> 00:02:47,443
which affects 160 million people 
globally, mostly in Sub-Saharan Africa.

47
00:02:48,811 --> 00:02:53,431
