63
00:03:51,882 --> 00:03:53,870
especially in urban areas.

64
00:03:54,817 --> 00:03:58,545
In both cases, the mosquitoes breed 
in certain types of water,

65
00:03:58,545 --> 00:04:01,762
and a control mechanism 
is to remove their habitat.

66
00:04:02,323 --> 00:04:06,077
